            <html:p><fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/jms-00CW.xml" title="Forester 3.0" addr="forest://forester/jms-00CW" type="local">Forester 3.0</fr:link> introduces a number of breaking changes to the source language in order to facilitate maintainability, diagnostic support, and extensibility of both the Forester tool and your individual <fr:link href="https://www.jonmsterling.com/foreign/forester/tfmt-000R.xml" title="Forests and trees of evergreen notes" addr="forest://forester/tfmt-000R" type="local">forests</fr:link>.</html:p>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
